<item>
            <title>[TIKA-2561] Tika Parser includes oudated/vulnerable version of JSoup</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/TIKA-2561</link>
                <project id="12310631" key="TIKA">Tika</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;org.apache.tika:tika-parsers:1.17 pulls in dependency JSoup&#160;1.7.2.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;JSoup versions older than 1.8.3 have a vulnerability in parsing.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2015-6748&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2015-6748&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
